      <title>北京对英伟达发出警告 中国 AI 芯片领军企业股价飙升 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/china-ai-chip-leader-soars-20-limit-as-beijing-warns-on-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社报道，北京方面正加大对国内企业的压力，要求其放弃英伟达处理器，转而使用本土替代品。周一，中国人工智能芯片制造商寒武纪科技股价飙升 20%，领涨该板块。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/china-ai-chip-leader-soars-20-limit-as-beijing-warns-on-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盛宝银行关闭香港办事处，理由是环境发生变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/saxo-closes-hong-kong-office-citing-changing-business-landscape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易平台盛宝银行 (Saxo Bank A/S) 正在关闭其位于香港的办事处，理由是这个陷入困境的金融中心的商业格局发生了变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/saxo-closes-hong-kong-office-citing-changing-business-landscape</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:48:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国汽车制造商 18 个月来在欧洲销售的电动汽车数量最少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/byd-saic-chinese-ev-sales-in-europe-lowest-in-more-than-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国制造商向欧洲客户销售的电动汽车数量是18个月以来最少的，8月份注册量较去年同期下降了近一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/byd-saic-chinese-ev-sales-in-europe-lowest-in-more-than-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众第二次发布盈利预警 暴露汽车制造商陷入衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/volkswagen-s-second-profit-warning-exposes-a-carmaker-in-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团三个月内第二次发布盈利预警，清楚地表明了一件事：欧洲最大的汽车制造商正在走下坡路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/volkswagen-s-second-profit-warning-exposes-a-carmaker-in-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国芯片库存以 2009 年以来最快的速度减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/south-korea-s-chip-stockpiles-shrink-at-fastest-pace-since-2009</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，韩国半导体库存以 2009 年以来最快的速度减少，表明对人工智能开发使用的高性能存储芯片的需求持续存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/south-korea-s-chip-stockpiles-shrink-at-fastest-pace-since-2009</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 00:56:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
